Class ViewProblemListFX.ProblemView

  • java.lang.Object
    • presentation.view.ViewProblemListFX.ProblemView
  • Enclosing class:
    ViewProblemListFX

    private static class ViewProblemListFX.ProblemView
extends java.lang.Object
    Inner class for holding information to be displayed in one row in the list of problems. Attributes: id: id of the problem type: type of the problem cells numRows: number of rows of the problem numColumns: number of columns of the problem difficulty: difficulty of the problem creator: creator of the problem
